          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "The hit PC drifting game ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Absolute Drift",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " finally arrives on the Switch at last. This self proclaimed zen game is something really special and presents a welcome challenge. Get ready for precise driving and lots of crashing/practice in this arcade style driving game focused entirely on the automotive art of drifting. Do you have the finesse to be a truly zen driver? ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "type": "embed",
        "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=A-jIc_Yz7RE",
        "html": "<iframe width=\"612\" height=\"344\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/A-jIc_Yz7RE?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>",
        "metadata": {
          "title": "Absolute Drift - Switch Release Trailer",
          "author_name": "Funselektor",
          "author_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCrNHgOBz_cGcH4YY9AQsAdA",
          "height": 344,
